SETTING UP PROJECT

//terminal:
sudo create-react-app app-name

//cd into app-name
npm start

---------------------------------------------------------------

IMPORTING BOOTSTRAP

//terminal:
npm i BOOTSTRAP

//index.js
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css';

----------------------------------------------------------------

GENERATE RANDOM IMAGE 

imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/200' 

----------------------------------------------------------------

APPLY CUSTOM STYLE TO ELEMENT

    style = {
        fontSize: 10,
        fontWeight: 'bold'
    };

    <span style={this.styles}">Hello World</span>
